graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Notebook Controller"
        Controller[OpenshiftNotebookReconciler<br/>Main Controller]
        Webhook[NotebookWebhook<br/>Mutating Webhook]
        WebhookServer[Webhook Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        MetricsServer[Metrics Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        HealthProbes[Health Probes<br/>8081/TCP HTTP]

        Controller -->|serves| WebhookServer
        Webhook -->|handles| WebhookServer
        Controller -->|exposes| MetricsServer
        Controller -->|provides| HealthProbes
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        NotebookCR[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources"
        Route[OpenShift Route<br/>HTTPS External Access]
        Service["Service: notebook-name-tls<br/>443/TCP ClusterIP"]
        Secret[OAuth Config Secret<br/>Cookie Secret]
        TLSSecret[TLS Secret<br/>service-ca provisioned]
        ConfigMap[ConfigMap<br/>Trusted CA Bundle]
        NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicies<br/>ctrl-np + oauth-np]
    end

    subgraph "Injected Sidecars"
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Container<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        KubeflowController[Kubeflow Notebook Controller<br/>Creates StatefulSets]
        OpenshiftRouter[OpenShift Router<br/>Ingress]
        OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>Authentication]
        ServiceCA[Service CA Operator<br/>Certificate Provisioning]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>SubjectAccessReview]
    end

    User[User] -->|creates| NotebookCR
    NotebookCR -->|watched by| Controller
    NotebookCR -->|mutated by| Webhook

    Controller -->|creates| Route
    Controller -->|creates| Service
    Controller -->|creates| Secret
    Controller -->|creates| TLSSecret
    Controller -->|creates| ConfigMap
    Controller -->|creates| NetworkPolicy

    Webhook -->|injects| OAuthProxy
    Webhook -->|reads proxy config| K8sAPI

    Controller -->|depends on| KubeflowController
    Route -->|processed by| OpenshiftRouter
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OAuthServer
    OAuthProxy -->|authorizes via| K8sAPI
    ServiceCA -->|provisions| TLSSecret

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthProxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KubeflowController fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OpenshiftRouter fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthServer fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceCA fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
